reviewText: a great naruto dvd well worth the price and the shipping was superb to boot any and every naruto fan and collector should have this if not then this is a must buy it is so well done
one of the best anime ever
my husband and I bought it to complete our collection of the series and we found that while it did arrive a bit late, it did meet our expectations
The seller was quick with the delivery process my husband and i are located in Germany and we recieved the movie in great condition.

We were almost worried for a second when our DVD Player didn't want to play it same with the PS2 and PS3 (Something about Regional Restricts) Though lucky that we got to see it is was intense and emotional. Loved seeing the story wrap up to a certain point, especially when they finally reunited with Sasuke, good though bad reunion it was, there was also some good action parts in it and was happy we got to see this awesome DVD.

The long wait is finaly over one of naruto's favorite characters is finaly here,Sasuke is back with new powers and a new look and naruto is ready to take him back to the village but sasuke isn't ready to go back just yet he still has some business to take care of. For naruto and his team thats not an option,trust me this dvd has some good episodes you won't be disappointed.
